## Germplasm Phenotype:
   - [bnt1-1]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Plants have dwarf stature,short hypocotyls, small rosettes with thick, round leaves, and reduced inflorescence and root systems. Plants are early senescent and have reduced fertility. Also has abnormal root hair development. Plants overexpress JA, SA, ABA and ethylene.
